<h4 id="sessionattributes">@SessionAttributes</h4>

<ul>
  <li>Х▀╔Е╦▄Ф°⌡Е°╗Е╓ Д╦╙Х╞╥Ф╠┌Д╧▀И≈╢Е┘╠Г■╗Ф÷░Д╦╙Ф╗║Е·▀Е╠·Ф─╖Ф∙╟Ф█╝О╪▄Е┬≥Е▐╞Д╩╔Е°╗  Ф▌╖Е┬╤Е≥╗Г╠╩Д╦┼Ф═┤ФЁ╗Д╦─Д╦╙ @SessionAttributes,Spring MVCЕ╟├Е°╗Ф╗║Е·▀Д╦╜Е╞╧Е╨■Г └Е╠·Ф─╖Ф ┌Е╜≤Е┬╟HttpSessionД╦╜</li>
  <li>@SessionAttributesИ≥╓Д╨├Е▐╞Д╩╔И─ Х©┤<strong>Е╠·Ф─╖Е░█</strong>Ф▄┤Е╝ И°─Х╕│Ф■╬Е┬╟Д╪   Х╞²Д╦╜Г └Е╠·Ф─╖Е╓√О╪▄Х©≤Е▐╞Д╩╔И─ Х©┤Ф╗║Е·▀Е╠·Ф─╖Г └<strong>Е╞╧Х╠║Г╠╩Е·▀</strong>Ф▄┤Е╝ Е⌠╙Д╨⌡  Ф╗║Е·▀Е╠·Ф─╖И°─Х╕│Ф■╬Е┬╟Д╪ Х╞²Д╦╜</li>
</ul>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>@SessionAttributes(types=User.class) Д╪ Е╟├И ░Е░╚Ф╗║Е·▀Д╦╜Ф┴─Ф°┴Г╠╩Е·▀Д╦╨ User.class Г └Е╠·Ф─╖Ф╥╩Е┼═Е┬╟Д╪ Х╞²Д╦╜Ц─┌
@SessionAttributes(value={Б─°user1Б─², Б─°user2Б─²})
@SessionAttributes(types={User.class, Dept.class})
@SessionAttributes(value={Б─°user1Б─², Б─°user2Б─²},  types={Dept.class})
</code></pre></div></div>

<div class="language-java highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nd">@Target</span><span class="o">(</span><span class="nc">ElementType</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="na">PARAMETER</span><span class="o">)</span>
<span class="nd">@Retention</span><span class="o">(</span><span class="nc">RetentionPolicy</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="na">RUNTIME</span><span class="o">)</span>
<span class="nd">@Documented</span>
<span class="kd">public</span> <span class="nd">@interface</span> <span class="nc">SessionAttribute</span> <span class="o">{</span>

	<span class="cm">/**
	 * Alias for {@link #name}.
	 */</span>
	<span class="nd">@AliasFor</span><span class="o">(</span><span class="s">"name"</span><span class="o">)</span>
	<span class="nc">String</span> <span class="nf">value</span><span class="o">()</span> <span class="k">default</span> <span class="s">""</span><span class="o">;</span>

	<span class="cm">/**
	 * The name of the session attribute to bind to.
	 * &lt;p&gt;The default name is inferred from the method parameter name.
	 */</span>
	<span class="nd">@AliasFor</span><span class="o">(</span><span class="s">"value"</span><span class="o">)</span>
	<span class="nc">String</span> <span class="nf">name</span><span class="o">()</span> <span class="k">default</span> <span class="s">""</span><span class="o">;</span>

	<span class="cm">/**
	 * Whether the session attribute is required.
	 * &lt;p&gt;Defaults to {@code true}, leading to an exception being thrown
	 * if the attribute is missing in the session or there is no session.
	 * Switch this to {@code false} if you prefer a {@code null} or Java 8
	 * {@code java.util.Optional} if the attribute doesn't exist.
	 */</span>
	<span class="kt">boolean</span> <span class="nf">required</span><span class="o">()</span> <span class="k">default</span> <span class="kc">true</span><span class="o">;</span>

<span class="o">}</span>

</code></pre></div></div>

<div class="language-java highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nd">@SessionAttributes</span><span class="o">(</span><span class="n">value</span><span class="o">={</span><span class="s">"user"</span><span class="o">},</span> <span class="n">types</span><span class="o">={</span><span class="nc">String</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="na">class</span><span class="o">})</span>
<span class="nd">@RequestMapping</span><span class="o">(</span><span class="s">"/springmvc"</span><span class="o">)</span>
<span class="nd">@Controller</span>
<span class="kd">public</span> <span class="kd">class</span> <span class="nc">SpringMVCTest</span> <span class="o">{</span>
	<span class="cm">/**
	 * @SessionAttributes И≥╓Д╨├Е▐╞Д╩╔И─ Х©┤Е╠·Ф─╖Е░█Ф▄┤Е╝ И°─Х╕│Ф■╬Е┬╟Д╪ Х╞²Д╦╜Г └Е╠·Ф─╖Е╓√(Е╝·И≥┘Д╦┼Д╫©Г■╗Г └Ф≤╞ value Е╠·Ф─╖Е─╪),
	 * Х©≤Е▐╞Д╩╔И─ Х©┤Ф╗║Е·▀Е╠·Ф─╖Г └Е╞╧Х╠║Г╠╩Е·▀Ф▄┤Е╝ Е⌠╙Д╨⌡Ф╗║Е·▀Е╠·Ф─╖И°─Х╕│Ф■╬Е┬╟Д╪ Х╞²Д╦╜(Е╝·И≥┘Д╦┼Д╫©Г■╗Г └Ф≤╞ types Е╠·Ф─╖Е─╪)
	 * 
	 * ФЁ╗Ф└▐: Х╞╔ФЁ╗Х╖ёЕ▐╙Х┐╫Ф■╬Е°╗Г╠╩Г └Д╦┼И²╒. Х─▄Д╦█Х┐╫Д©╝И╔╟Ф■╬Ф√╧ФЁ∙. 
	 */</span>
	<span class="nd">@RequestMapping</span><span class="o">(</span><span class="s">"/testSessionAttributes"</span><span class="o">)</span>
	<span class="kd">public</span> <span class="nc">String</span> <span class="nf">testSessionAttributes</span><span class="o">(</span><span class="nc">Map</span><span class="o">&lt;</span><span class="nc">String</span><span class="o">,</span> <span class="nc">Object</span><span class="o">&gt;</span> <span class="n">map</span><span class="o">){</span>
		<span class="nc">User</span> <span class="n">user</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="k">new</span> <span class="nc">User</span><span class="o">(</span><span class="s">"Tom"</span><span class="o">,</span> <span class="s">"123456"</span><span class="o">,</span> <span class="s">"tom@atguigu.com"</span><span class="o">,</span> <span class="mi">15</span><span class="o">);</span>
		<span class="n">map</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="na">put</span><span class="o">(</span><span class="s">"user"</span><span class="o">,</span> <span class="n">user</span><span class="o">);</span>
		<span class="n">map</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="na">put</span><span class="o">(</span><span class="s">"school"</span><span class="o">,</span> <span class="s">"atguigu"</span><span class="o">);</span>
		<span class="k">return</span> <span class="no">SUCCESS</span><span class="o">;</span>
	<span class="o">}</span>
<span class="o">}</span>

</code></pre></div></div>

<h4 id="Е╪┌Е╦╦">Е╪┌Е╦╦</h4>

<ul>
  <li>SpringMVCД╪ Е┘┬Д╩▌Ф═┤ФЁ╗ @ModelAttribute ФЁ╗Х╖ёГ └Ф√╧ФЁ∙И┤▄И²╒Е▌╩Ф┴╬О╪▄Ф÷╔Ф┴╬Ф≤╞Е░╕Ф°┴Е╞╧Е╨■Г └Е─╪О╪▄Е╕┌Ф·°Ф╡║Ф°┴ О╪▄Е┬≥Д╪ Е╪╨Е┬╤Д╩▌@SessionAttributesИ┤▄И²╒Е▌╩Ф┴╬О╪▄Е╕┌Ф·°Х©≤Ф╡║Ф°┴Ф┴╬Е┬╟О╪▄И┌ёД╧┬Е╟╠Д╪ Ф┼⌡Е┤╨Е╪┌Е╦╦</li>
</ul>

<h4 id="modelattribute">@ModelAttribute</h4>

<ul>
  <li>Е°╗Ф√╧ФЁ∙Е╝ Д╧┴Д╦┼Д╫©Г■╗ @ModelAttribute ФЁ╗Х╖ёО╪ Spring MVCЕ°╗Х╟┐Г■╗Г⌡╝Ф═┤Е╓└Г░├Ф√╧ФЁ∙Е┴█О╪▄Д╪ Е┘┬И─░Д╦╙Х╟┐Г■╗Е°╗Ф√╧ФЁ∙Г╨╖Д╦┼Ф═┤ФЁ╗Д╨├@ModelAttributeГ └Ф√╧ФЁ∙</li>
  <li>Е°╗Ф√╧ФЁ∙Г └Е┘╔Е▐┌Е┴█Д╫©Г■╗ @ModelAttribute ФЁ╗Х╖ёО╪ Е▐╞Д╩╔Д╩▌И ░Е░╚Е╞╧Х╠║Д╦╜Х▌╥Е▐√И ░Е░╚Г └Ф╗║Е·▀Ф∙╟Ф█╝Д╦╜Х▌╥Е▐√Е╞╧Х╠║О╪▄Е├█Е╟├Х╞╥Ф╠┌Е▐┌Ф∙╟Г╩▒Е╝ Е┬╟Е╞╧Х╠║Д╦╜О╪▄Е├█Д╪═Е┘╔Е┘╔Е▐┌.Е╟├Ф√╧ФЁ∙Е┘╔Е▐┌Е╞╧Х╠║Ф╥╩Е┼═Е┬╟Ф╗║Е·▀Д╦╜</li>
</ul>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>	&lt;!--  
		Ф╗║Ф▀÷Д©╝Ф■╧Ф⌠█Д╫°
		1. Е▌÷Е╖▀Ф∙╟Ф█╝Д╦╨: 1, Tom, 123456,tom@atguigu.com,12
		2. Е╞├Г═│Д╦█Х┐╫Х╒╚Д©╝Ф■╧.
		3. Х║╗Е█∙Е⌡·Ф≤╬, Ф╗║Ф▀÷Ф⌠█Д╫°Г⌡╢Ф▌╔Е°╗Х║╗Е█∙Е║╚Е├≥Е╞╧Е╨■Г └Е╠·Ф─╖Е─╪
	--&gt;
	&lt;form action="springmvc/testModelAttribute" method="Post"&gt;
		&lt;input type="hidden" name="id" value="1"/&gt;
		username: &lt;input type="text" name="username" value="Tom"/&gt;
		&lt;br&gt;
		email: &lt;input type="text" name="email" value="tom@atguigu.com"/&gt;
		&lt;br&gt;
		age: &lt;input type="text" name="age" value="12"/&gt;
		&lt;br&gt;
		&lt;input type="submit" value="Submit"/&gt;
	&lt;/form&gt;

</code></pre></div></div>

<div class="language-java highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>
	<span class="cm">/**
	 * 1. Ф°┴ @ModelAttribute Ф═┤Х╝╟Г └Ф√╧ФЁ∙, Д╪ Е°╗Ф╞▐Д╦╙Г⌡╝Ф═┤Ф√╧ФЁ∙Ф┴╖Х║▄Д╧▀Е┴█Х╒╚ SpringMVC Х╟┐Г■╗! 
	 * 2. @ModelAttribute ФЁ╗Х╖ёД╧÷Е▐╞Д╩╔Ф²╔Д©╝И╔╟Г⌡╝Ф═┤Ф√╧ФЁ∙ POJO Г╠╩Е·▀Г └Е┘╔Е▐┌, Е┘╤ value Е╠·Ф─╖Е─╪Ф°┴Е╕┌Д╦▀Г └Д╫°Г■╗:
	 * 1). SpringMVC Д╪ Д╫©Г■╗ value Е╠·Ф─╖Е─╪Е°╗ implicitModel Д╦╜Ф÷╔Ф┴╬Е╞╧Е╨■Г └Е╞╧Х╠║, Х▀╔Е╜≤Е°╗Е┬≥Д╪ Г⌡╢Ф▌╔Д╪═Е┘╔Е┬╟Г⌡╝Ф═┤Ф√╧ФЁ∙Г └Е┘╔Е▐┌Д╦╜.
	 * 2). SpringMVC Д╪ Д╩╔ value Д╦╨ key, POJO Г╠╩Е·▀Г └Е╞╧Х╠║Д╦╨ value, Е╜≤Е┘╔Е┬╟ request Д╦╜. 
	 */</span>
	<span class="nd">@ModelAttribute</span>
	<span class="kd">public</span> <span class="kt">void</span> <span class="nf">getUser</span><span class="o">(</span><span class="nd">@RequestParam</span><span class="o">(</span><span class="n">value</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s">"id"</span><span class="o">,</span><span class="n">required</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="kc">false</span><span class="o">)</span> <span class="nc">Integer</span> <span class="n">id</span><span class="o">,</span> 
			<span class="nc">Map</span><span class="o">&lt;</span><span class="nc">String</span><span class="o">,</span> <span class="nc">Object</span><span class="o">&gt;</span> <span class="n">map</span><span class="o">){</span>
		<span class="nc">System</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="na">out</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="na">println</span><span class="o">(</span><span class="s">"modelAttribute method"</span><span class="o">);</span>
		<span class="k">if</span><span class="o">(</span><span class="n">id</span> <span class="o">!=</span> <span class="kc">null</span><span class="o">){</span>
			<span class="c1">//Ф╗║Ф▀÷Д╩▌Ф∙╟Ф█╝Е╨⌠Д╦╜Х▌╥Е▐√Е╞╧Х╠║</span>
			<span class="nc">User</span> <span class="n">user</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="k">new</span> <span class="nc">User</span><span class="o">(</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="o">,</span> <span class="s">"Tom"</span><span class="o">,</span> <span class="s">"123456"</span><span class="o">,</span> <span class="s">"tom@atguigu.com"</span><span class="o">,</span> <span class="mi">12</span><span class="o">);</span>
			<span class="nc">System</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="na">out</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="na">println</span><span class="o">(</span><span class="s">"Д╩▌Ф∙╟Ф█╝Е╨⌠Д╦╜Х▌╥Е▐√Д╦─Д╦╙Е╞╧Х╠║: "</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="n">user</span><span class="o">);</span>
			
			<span class="n">map</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="na">put</span><span class="o">(</span><span class="s">"user"</span><span class="o">,</span> <span class="n">user</span><span class="o">);</span>
		<span class="o">}</span>
	<span class="o">}</span>
	
	<span class="cm">/**
	  Х©░Х║▄Ф╣│Г╗▀:
	  1. Ф┴╖Х║▄ @ModelAttribute ФЁ╗Х╖ёД©╝И╔╟Г └Ф√╧ФЁ∙: Д╩▌Ф∙╟Ф█╝Е╨⌠Д╦╜Е▐√Е┤╨Е╞╧Х╠║, Ф┼┼Е╞╧Х╠║Ф■╬Е┘╔Е┬╟Д╨├ Map Д╦╜. И■╝Д╦╨: user
	  2. SpringMVC Д╩▌ Map Д╦╜Е▐√Е┤╨ User Е╞╧Х╠║, Е╧╤Ф┼┼Х║╗Е█∙Г └Х╞╥Ф╠┌Е▐┌Ф∙╟Х╣▀Г╩≥Х╞╔ User Е╞╧Х╠║Г └Е╞╧Е╨■Е╠·Ф─╖.
	  3. SpringMVC Ф┼┼Д╦┼Х©╟Е╞╧Х╠║Д╪═Е┘╔Г⌡╝Ф═┤Ф√╧ФЁ∙Г └Е▐┌Ф∙╟. 
	  
	  ФЁ╗Ф└▐: Е°╗ @ModelAttribute Д©╝И╔╟Г └Ф√╧ФЁ∙Д╦╜, Ф■╬Е┘╔Е┬╟ Map Ф≈╤Г └И■╝И°─Х╕│Е▓▄Г⌡╝Ф═┤Ф√╧ФЁ∙Е┘╔Е▐┌Г╠╩Е·▀Г └Г╛╛Д╦─Д╦╙Е╜≈Ф╞█Е╟▐Е├≥Г └Е╜≈Г╛╕Д╦╡Д╦─Х┤╢!
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------	  
	  SpringMVC Г║╝Е╝ Г⌡╝Ф═┤Ф√╧ФЁ∙ POJO Г╠╩Е·▀Е┘╔Е▐┌Г └Х©┤Г╗▀
	  1. Г║╝Е╝ Д╦─Д╦╙ key:
	  1). Х▀╔Г⌡╝Ф═┤Ф√╧ФЁ∙Г └ POJO Г╠╩Е·▀Г └Е▐┌Ф∙╟Ф°╗Ф°┴Д╫©Г■╗ @ModelAttribute Д╫°Д╦╨Д©╝И╔╟, Е┬≥ key Д╦╨ POJO Г╠╩Е░█Г╛╛Д╦─Д╦╙Е╜≈Ф╞█Г └Е╟▐Е├≥
	  2). Х▀╔Д╫©Г■╗Д╨├  @ModelAttribute Ф²╔Д©╝И╔╟, Е┬≥ key Д╦╨ @ModelAttribute ФЁ╗Х╖ёГ └ value Е╠·Ф─╖Е─╪. 
	  
	  2. Е°╗ implicitModel Д╦╜Ф÷╔Ф┴╬ key Е╞╧Е╨■Г └Е╞╧Х╠║, Х▀╔Е╜≤Е°╗, Е┬≥Д╫°Д╦╨Е┘╔Е▐┌Д╪═Е┘╔
	  1). Х▀╔Е°╗ @ModelAttribute Ф═┤Х╝╟Г └Ф√╧ФЁ∙Д╦╜Е°╗ Map Д╦╜Д©²Е╜≤Х©┤, Д╦■ key Е▓▄ 1 Г║╝Е╝ Г └ key Д╦─Х┤╢, Е┬≥Д╪ Х▌╥Е▐√Е┬╟. 
	  
	  3. Х▀╔ implicitModel Д╦╜Д╦█Е╜≤Е°╗ key Е╞╧Е╨■Г └Е╞╧Х╠║, Е┬≥Фё─Ф÷╔Е╫⌠Е┴█Г └ Handler Ф≤╞Е░╕Д╫©@SessionAttributes ФЁ╗Х╖ёД©╝И╔╟, Х▀╔Д╫©Г■╗Д╨├Х╞╔ФЁ╗Х╖ё, Д╦■ @SessionAttributes ФЁ╗Х╖ёГ └ value Е╠·Ф─╖Е─╪Д╦╜Е▄┘Е░╚Д╨├ key, Е┬≥Д╪ Д╩▌HttpSession Д╦╜Ф²╔Х▌╥Е▐√ key Ф┴─Е╞╧Е╨■Г └ value Е─╪, Х▀╔Е╜≤Е°╗Е┬≥Г⌡╢Ф▌╔Д╪═Е┘╔Е┬╟Г⌡╝Ф═┤Ф√╧ФЁ∙Г └Е┘╔Е▐┌Д╦╜. Х▀╔Д╦█Е╜≤Е°╗Е┬≥Е╟├Ф┼⌡Е┤╨Е╪┌Е╦╦. 
	  
	  4. Х▀╔ Handler Ф╡║Ф°┴Ф═┤Х╞├ @SessionAttributes ФЁ╗Х╖ёФ┬√ @SessionAttributes ФЁ╗Х╖ёГ └ value Е─╪Д╦╜Д╦█Е▄┘Е░╚ key, Е┬≥Д╪ И─ Х©┤Е▐█Е╟└Ф²╔Е┬⌡Е╩╨ POJO Г╠╩Е·▀Г └Е▐┌Ф∙╟, Д╪═Е┘╔Д╦╨Г⌡╝Ф═┤Ф√╧ФЁ∙Г └Е▐┌Ф∙╟
	  
	  5. SpringMVC Д╪ Ф┼┼ key Е▓▄ POJO Г╠╩Е·▀Г └Е╞╧Х╠║Д©²Е╜≤Е┬╟ implicitModel Д╦╜, Х©⌡Х─▄Д╪ Д©²Е╜≤Е┬╟ request Д╦╜. 

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
	  Ф╨░Д╩ёГ═│Е┬├Ф·░Г └Ф╣│Г╗▀
	  1. Х╟┐Г■╗ @ModelAttribute ФЁ╗Х╖ёД©╝И╔╟Г └Ф√╧ФЁ∙. Е╝·И≥┘Д╦┼Ф┼┼ @ModelAttribute Ф√╧ФЁ∙Д╦╜ Map Д╦╜Г └Ф∙╟Ф█╝Ф■╬Е°╗Д╨├ implicitModel Д╦╜.
	  2. Х╖ёФ·░Х╞╥Ф╠┌Е╓└Г░├Е≥╗Г └Г⌡╝Ф═┤Е▐┌Ф∙╟, Е╝·И≥┘Д╦┼Х╞╔Г⌡╝Ф═┤Е▐┌Ф∙╟Ф²╔Х┤╙Д╨▌ WebDataBinder Е╞╧Х╠║Г └ target Е╠·Ф─╖
	  1). Е┬⌡Е╩╨ WebDataBinder Е╞╧Х╠║:
	  Б▒═. Г║╝Е╝  objectName Е╠·Ф─╖: Х▀╔Д╪═Е┘╔Г └ attrName Е╠·Ф─╖Е─╪Д╦╨ "", Е┬≥ objectName Д╦╨Г╠╩Е░█Г╛╛Д╦─Д╦╙Е╜≈Ф╞█Е╟▐Е├≥. 
	 ФЁ╗Ф└▐: attrName. Х▀╔Г⌡╝Ф═┤Ф√╧ФЁ∙Г └ POJO Е╠·Ф─╖Д╫©Г■╗Д╨├ @ModelAttribute Ф²╔Д©╝И╔╟, Е┬≥ attrName Е─╪Е█ЁД╦╨ @ModelAttribute Г └ value Е╠·Ф─╖Е─╪ 
	  
	  Б▒║. Г║╝Е╝  target Е╠·Ф─╖:
	  	 Е°╗ implicitModel Д╦╜Ф÷╔Ф┴╬ attrName Е╞╧Е╨■Г └Е╠·Ф─╖Е─╪. Х▀╔Е╜≤Е°╗, okО╪▄Х▀╔Д╦█Е╜≤Е°╗: Е┬≥И╙▄Х╞│Е╫⌠Е┴█ Handler Ф≤╞Е░╕Д╫©Г■╗Д╨├ @SessionAttributes Х©⌡Х║▄Д©╝И╔╟, Х▀╔Д╫©Г■╗Д╨├, Е┬≥Е╟²Х╞∙Д╩▌ Session Д╦╜Х▌╥Е▐√ attrName Ф┴─Е╞╧Е╨■Г └Е╠·Ф─╖Е─╪. Х▀╔ session Д╦╜Ф╡║Ф°┴Е╞╧Е╨■Г └Е╠·Ф─╖Е─╪, Е┬≥Ф┼⌡Е┤╨Д╨├Е╪┌Е╦╦.  Х▀╔ Handler Ф╡║Ф°┴Д╫©Г■╗ @SessionAttributes Х©⌡Х║▄Д©╝И╔╟, Ф┬√ @SessionAttributes Д╦╜Ф╡║Ф°┴Д╫©Г■╗ value Е─╪Ф▄┤Е╝ Г └ keyЕ▓▄ attrName Г⌡╦Е▄╧И┘█, Е┬≥И─ Х©┤Е▐█Е╟└Е┬⌡Е╩╨Д╨├ POJO Е╞╧Х╠║
	  
	  2). SpringMVC Ф┼┼Х║╗Е█∙Г └Х╞╥Ф╠┌Е▐┌Ф∙╟Х╣▀Г╩≥Д╨├ WebDataBinder Г └ target Е╞╧Е╨■Г └Е╠·Ф─╖. 
	  3). SpringMVC Д╪ Ф┼┼ WebDataBinder Г └ attrName Е▓▄ target Г╩≥Е┬╟ implicitModel. 
	  Х©▒Х─▄Д╪═Е┬╟ request Е÷÷Е╞╧Х╠║Д╦╜. 
